1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,100
WindWalker is a GPT-powered web app builder for small businesses.

2
00:00:05,100 --> 00:00:12,400
A user describes the business they want to run: for example,
a digital bookstore with member login, cart, checkout, and purchase history.

3
00:00:12,400 --> 00:00:19,150
The app also includes downloads and an operator dashboard.

4
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:28,850
WindWalker turns that request into a workflow pattern
and generates a responsive web app preview.

5
00:00:28,850 --> 00:00:38,330
It lets the user refine the app through conversation.
When ready, the app is deployed to Cloudflare Pages as a live URL.

6
00:00:39,650 --> 00:00:51,300
In this demo, the deployed bookstore supports mock member login,
product browsing, cart interaction, and test checkout.

7
00:00:51,700 --> 00:01:15,900
The same workflow can be adapted for bookings, quotes, customer intake,
support, and other small-business operations.

8
00:01:16,250 --> 00:01:26,400
We used GPT-5.6 for final iteration and validation,
with OpenAI Codex supporting implementation, testing, and submission evidence.

9
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:42,742
GPT can generate an app. WindWalker helps small-business owners launch,
operate, fix, and continuously improve it with lightweight human support.
